name: Benchmark Reclaimed Canvas Wash Bag
description:
Benchmark (Love Bug) Reclaimed Canvas Cosmetic Bag hand printed with love.

This canvas wash-bag with leather trim has a water resistant black lining and features a colourful and varied selection of sample screen prints which adds to it's charm- Making each bag different from the other, but all will display the 'LOVE' print as the main design. We can not guarantee an exact copy as each bag is individual.

Perfect gift for eco warriors, quirky eclectics and people who just love colour.

Made from:
This wash-bag is made from 100 % cotton canvas reclaimed from our screen-printing tables which feature displaced prints and a polyester lining. Designed here in the UK, made in India which carry the fair trade kite mark then printed and finished here again in our London studio.

Size: 22cm (W) x 25cm (D)

name: Metallic Leather Bow Wrist-Cuff
description:
Gorgeous leather Bow cuff that doubles up as a stylish table keepsake.

If you like the biker chick look, but wish for a more feminine style, accessorise with this pretty leather bow wrist cuff, perfect for those who can't do dainty. Or be a super stylish host and gift them as favours for style-savvy dinner party guests by wrapping around their napkins, a great tableware decoration. Suitable for Christmas stocking fillers, hen do's and birthday tea parties.

Hand screen print on super soft nappa leather, with a gathered effect in the shape of a bow.

Available in chocolate brown, peach metallic, gold metallic, mustard yellow and black leather.


Made from:
All materials including components are sourced locally and all leather used is a by-product from the food industry and reclaimed from off-cuts. This poduct was specifically created to reduce the amount of waste produced from our seasonal collections.

Dimensions:
Approx. 19cm x 5cm- One size. The tighter the fit the better, the leather will mould with the warmth of your wrist.
